My first goal after setup was to use OpenClaw to analyze my files and see if we could optimize my storage.

However, in a matter of minutes, with only a small number of chat requests, I managed to run up an unexpected **$44.08 agent API bill**. This article details how this could happen, and what lessons I can share to prevent it ever happening again.

---

