    				The conversation sat completely idle for nearly a day and a half. This caused a cache (Gemini Context Cache) used by the agent on the server to expire. The very next prompt was forced to perform a complete "cold start" and re-upload the bloated history, triggering premium uncached billing rates instead of the usual 90% warm-cache discount.
