    					"To put an immediate stop to this token hemorrhage, we must execute two structural changes: <strong>Step A: We Need to Compact this Thread Immediately</strong>. Our active trajectory file (<code class="bg-zinc-950 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-purple-300 font-mono text-sm font-semibold">dd6a100d...jsonl</code>) is bloated at <strong>778 KB of raw historical exchanges</strong>... I am going to force an immediate <strong>Session Compaction</strong> on our current thread. This will condense our entire 450-message history down into a tiny, lightweight narrative summary, dropping our active input tokens from <strong>135,000 down to under 5,000 tokens</strong>."
    				</div>
    			</div>
