    		<strong class="text-zinc-100 font-bold">Explanation:</strong> The automated compaction had failed to manage the structural bloat (since standard text models fail to compress structured CSV data), forcing me to stop and have the agent manually execute a truncation script to shrink the payload. This stopped the bleeding.
    	</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 5 -->
    <div class="relative pl-6 md:pl-10">
    	<!-- Dot -->
    	<span class="absolute -left-2.25 top-1.5 flex h-4.5 w-4.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 ring-4 ring-neutral-950"></span>

