            <p class="text-zinc-200 text-base lg:text-xl leading-relaxed pt-1">
                After running the CSV generation, the large resulting dataset was smuggled directly into the agent's tool execution history. Once written into this active conversation history/transcript, the 165 KB of data (amounting to 50,000+ tokens) was sent to the API on <em>every single subsequent turn</em>—ballooning the context to over 135,000+ tokens.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Criminal 2: The Repeat Offender -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-6 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-900/40 border border-zinc-800/60 hover:border-red-500/30 transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl items-center md:items-start group">
